#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Martenweave Development AI Factory harness.

Stdlib-only command harness for the factory documented in docs/factory/.
It orchestrates existing commands (pytest, ruff, martenweave, demo scripts, npm,
gh) and never implements product logic, never writes code or canonical data, and
never mutates GitHub state. See docs/factory/README.md for the loop and
docs/factory/policies/QUALITY_GATES.md for the gate definitions.

Commands:
    audit          L0 inspection: repo freshness, structure, doc/skill validators
    plan           Rank open agent-ready issues into a recommended next task
    run-next       Print the execution brief for the top-ranked issue
    review         Diff hygiene checks + critical-review checklist for current work
    validate       Run deterministic gates G3-G10
    release-check  Gather G11 release evidence (read-only)

Every command supports --json for machine-readable output.
"""

